{"tid":2410974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂新年假期後確診急升　曾祈殷指禁聚措施或須再收緊","createTime":"2021-02-17T04:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T05:24:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64ab53c28d33386c698a7beda4297618b1590d7a","tid":2410974,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"本港昨(16日)新增8宗確診個案，但初步確診就約有20宗，顯示疫情依然反覆。醫學會傳染病顧問委員會聯席主席曾祈殷今早(17日)在電台節目表示，農曆新年假期可能令數據有滯後，加上過年期間很多人聚會及拜年，要觀察未來14日情況，審視疫情有否反彈徵兆。<br />\n<br />\n對於部分社交距離措施明日(18日)起放寬，曾認為政府是在平衡防疫、經濟及本地就業情況下作出決定，但強調確診數字若連續一星期出現不尋常的急升趨勢，政府須作出適當調整。"},{"pid":"1ba6396dd20ff071d74f1ecb069d5ac8ca4dcac9","tid":2410974,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"發神經  連尖都唔畀人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07391bbcd55dd782bf5b2d3cbf753f664f68b4d","tid":2410974,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"過年班柒頭唔走去驗<br />\n根本冇斷過<br />\n<br />\n過完年又唔知傳左俾幾多個親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e35a32e92a0fdd7d8f448a045ba72e4f0c4977","tid":2410974,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"放假令疫情回升, 返工就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8679e7c9b103ec69220674a746170570119e7c2c","tid":2410974,"uid":271981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07391bbcd55dd782bf5b2d3cbf753f664f68b4d","tid":2410974,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"過年班柒頭唔走去驗<br />\n根本冇斷過<br />\n<br />\n過完年又唔知傳左俾幾多個親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:48:00.000Z",